---
import { CONTACT_EMAIL, CONTACT_PHONE, SITE_HOST, SITE_URL } from "@config";
import SectionTitle from "../section_title/index.astro";

const phoneUri = CONTACT_PHONE.replace(/[^\d+]/g, "");
const signatureHtml = `<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="font-family:Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:#0E0E0E;">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding-right:20px;border-right:2px solid #FF5B1F;vertical-align:middle;">
      <div style="width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:14px;background:#0E0E0E;color:#FFF;font-family:Fredoka,sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:44px;text-align:center;line-height:72px;">m✦</div>
    </td>
    <td style="padding-left:20px;vertical-align:middle;">
      <div style="font-family:Fredoka,sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;">Luis Ramírez</div>
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:#7A7A7A;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;">Fundador · Muéstrate</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#3D3D3D;margin-top:10px;">
        <a href="tel:${phoneUri}" style="color:#3D3D3D;text-decoration:none;">${CONTACT_PHONE}</a> ·
        <a href="mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}" style="color:#3D3D3D;text-decoration:none;">${CONTACT_EMAIL}</a> ·
        <a href="${SITE_URL}" style="color:#3D3D3D;text-decoration:none;">${SITE_HOST}</a>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px;font-size:12px;color:#FF5B1F;font-family:Fredoka;">Tu negocio online en 48h. Así de simple.</div>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>`;
---

<section class="bg-paper-warm pb-24 md:pb-32">
  <div class="container-shell">
    <SectionTitle title="Horizontal — uso diario" />
    <article class="brand-outline overflow-hidden rounded-brand-lg bg-paper shadow-brand-lg">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span></div>
        <span>Re: propuesta web · {SITE_HOST}</span>
        <span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-ink">
        <div class="mb-7 max-w-xl">
          <p>Hola Rosa,</p>
          <p class="mt-3">Adjunto la propuesta para la web de tu barbería. Cualquier consulta me avisas por acá o por WhatsApp.</p>
          <p class="mt-3">Abrazo,</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex max-w-2xl items-center gap-5">
          <div class="grid size-[72px] shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-brand-md bg-ink font-display text-4xl font-bold text-paper">m✦</div>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-orange pl-5">
            <div class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-normal">Luis Ramírez</div>
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.04em] text-gray-500">Fundador · Muéstrate</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <a href={`tel:${CONTACT_PHONE.replace(/[^\d+]/g, "")}`}>{CONTACT_PHONE}</a>
              <span class="mx-2 text-gray-300">·</span>
              <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
              <span class="mx-2 text-gray-300">·</span>
              <a href={SITE_URL}>{SITE_HOST}</a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-2 font-display text-xs font-medium text-orange">Tu negocio online en 48h. Así de simple.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <details class="mt-4">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer text-sm font-bold text-gray-700">Ver HTML para pegar en Gmail / Outlook →</summary>
      <pre class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-brand-md bg-ink p-5 text-xs leading-6 text-gray-200"><code>{signatureHtml}</code></pre>
    </details>

    <SectionTitle title="Card oscura — propuestas & ventas" />
    <article class="brand-outline overflow-hidden rounded-brand-lg bg-paper shadow-brand-lg">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span></div>
        <span>Propuesta web — Ceviches del Puerto</span>
        <span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 text-sm leading-7 text-ink">
        <p>Jhon, qué tal.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">Te mando la propuesta de la web + el link de pago. Tu página queda lista el viernes.</p>
        <div class="mt-8 max-w-lg rounded-brand-md bg-ink p-6 text-paper">
          <div class="flex justify-between gap-6">
            <div>
              <div class="font-display text-xl font-semibold tracking-normal">Luis Ramírez</div>
              <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.06em] text-gray-300">Fundador · Estrategia</div>
              <div class="mt-4 grid gap-1 text-xs text-gray-200">
                <p>✉ {CONTACT_EMAIL}</p>
                <p>📱 {CONTACT_PHONE}</p>
                <p>🌐 {SITE_HOST}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
              <div class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-orange">muéstrate✦</div>
              <span class="mt-2 inline-flex rounded-full bg-orange px-3 py-1 text-[0.65rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">● 48h</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <SectionTitle title="Minimal — respuestas rápidas" />
    <article class="brand-outline overflow-hidden rounded-brand-lg bg-paper shadow-brand-lg">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-gray-200 bg-gray-100 px-5 py-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
        <div class="flex gap-1.5"><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span><span class="size-2.5 rounded-full bg-gray-300"></span></div>
        <span>Re: ¿Hasta cuándo la promo?</span>
        <span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="p-8 text-sm leading-7 text-ink">
        <p>Hasta el 30 de abril. Si quieres te bloqueo la fecha hoy mismo.</p>
        <div class="mt-7 border-l-[3px] border-orange pl-4">
          <div class="font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-normal">Luis Ramírez</div>
          <div class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500">Fundador · Muéstrate</div>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <a href={`tel:${CONTACT_PHONE.replace(/[^\d+]/g, "")}`}>{CONTACT_PHONE}</a>
            <span class="mx-2 text-gray-300">|</span>
            <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-display text-base font-semibold">muéstrate<span class="text-orange">✦</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <div class="mt-10 rounded-brand-lg bg-ink p-6 text-paper">
      <strong class="font-display text-lg font-semibold">Cómo instalarla</strong>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
        Copia el HTML de la variante que quieras y pégalo en Configuración → Firma en Gmail, Outlook o Apple Mail. Las tres versiones usan colores hex inline para máxima compatibilidad.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
